## ğŸ“ Project Setup

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

3. Start the project:

```bash
npx expo start
```

4. For testing on mobile:

```bash
npx expo start --lan
```

Then scan the QR code using Expo Go on your phone

